          "settings": {
            "number": "05 — EMPOWERMENT",
            "title": "The Architect of Sovereignty",
            "body": "Generic empowerment is a commodity; localized sovereignty is the new global currency. In this high-impact session, Nancy Vuu equips visionary women to stop seeking permission and start architecting a sovereign, uncompromising command. Leveraging her proprietary blueprint from refugee to global runways, Nancy deconstructs the barriers between raw passion and realized authority. Discover how to forge an unbreakable alliance between your profound spirit and your visibility, leveraging your unique visionary voice not just to lead, but to command a massive, unshakeable legacy for the global good. It is time to don the mantle of your true distinction."
          }
        },
        "pillar_6": {
          "type": "pillar",
          "settings": {
            "number": "06 — EXCELLENCE",
            "title": "Dream Again",
            "body": "Refuse to let your past dictate your future; it is time to architect a legacy of absolute significance. Based on the unfiltered masterclass of her book, Let There Be Fashion, Nancy Vuu presents \"Dream Again\"—the proprietary blueprint for deconstructing the barriers between mere survival and divine significance. Tracing her harrowing journey from childhood refugee to commanding the global stages of Cannes, Nancy empowers the visionary community and thought leaders to merge profound spiritual conviction with unapologetic artistry. Through stirring narratives and hard-won wisdom, discover how a single, courageous \"yes\" can unlock doors across the world, enabling you to design your destiny and inhabit your highest potential."
          }
